HEADWORD: Dogcart
<hw>Dog"cart`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A light one-horse
carriage, commonly two-wheeled, patterned after a cart. The original
dogcarts used in England by sportsmen had a box at the back for carrying
dogs.</def></p>

